    public class UiCheckBoxes<T>
extends UiMultiSelectionButtonGroup<T,UiCheckBoxes<T>>
    A group of checkboxes that have a selection state that can be toggled independent from each other (other than UiRadioButtons where the selection is mutually exclusive). The datatype defines the type of the button labels. Typically string and enum values are supported.
